Onyeisi  Innocent Ifediaso Chukwuma (amuru ya na afo 1961 na Nnewi, Anambra) onye Nigeria , obukwa onye azumahia.

CAREER:
Dezie N'afọ 1981, mgbe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ, Innocent malitere ịzụ ahịa na akụrụngwa, azụmahịa na-enye nnukwu ego na South East Nigeria
O wee hiwe ụlọ ọrụ Innoson Group na Innoson Manufacturing, Innoson Tech
Ltd dị ka ndị enyemaka ya
Na 2013, a họpụtara ya onye osote onye isi oche, Board of Trustees National Coalition for Jonathan/Sambo Presidency, otu na-akwalite ntuli aka nke onye isi ala Naijiria, Goodluck Jonathan.
